# 🚀 Instalação

## Criar ambiente virtual

```
python3 -m venv market-qwan-env
source market-qwan-env/bin/activate
```

## Instalar dependências

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

# ▶ Rodar Backtest Local

```
python main.py
```

---

# ▶ Rodar Dashboard Streamlit

```
streamlit run dashboard.py
```

---

# ▶ Rodar Dashboard Dash

```
python dash_app.py
```

